    "notes": [
      "P0, P1 and P2 are large analog-capable ring pads.",
      "P5 and P11 are shared with buttons A and B.",
      "P19/P20 expose the external I2C bus.",
      "The simulated LED matrix uses one logical pin per pixel to avoid adding board-specific multiplexing to the core."
    ]
